# Kit (formerly ConvertKit) form for the email waitlist.
#
# This is the NUMERIC form id — it is public (it appears in the page's HTML),
# so it is safe to commit/expose. NOT your API key.
#
# Where to find it: Kit dashboard → Grow → Landing Pages & Forms → create or
# open a Form → the number in the editor URL (app.kit.com/forms/designers/<ID>/edit)
# is the id. It's also the <ID> in the embed action URL
# https://app.convertkit.com/forms/<ID>/subscriptions
#
# The live form id (9503947) is committed as the default in src/components/
# Signup.astro, so the site works without any .env. Only set this to OVERRIDE
# that default — e.g. point local dev or a staging build at a different form.
PUBLIC_KIT_FORM_ID=
